how both stay isolated from the ledger's internal locking/crash-safety
mechanics in ssm/design/source-registry so those internals can change without
changing either calling contract. Apply the
settled fetch-admission, MIME-representation, and fresh-source-refetch
policies plus the settled batch-atomicity contract: a caller-targeted fresh
source re-fetches, while refresh-stale remains stale/absent-only. Row outcomes
must name the lifecycle stage reached and carry the settled structured
source-health diagnostic when one exists, not conceal a fetch, representation,
ledger, index, or control-plane failure as an ordinary success.
